data.description: This charming home offers the perfect blend of comfort and style in a fantastic, desirable neighborhood. The numerous upgrades throughout add to this already cozy, adorable space. The privacy fence envelopes the backyard, creating a serene retreat for you and your family to enjoy and the shed for extra storage!! NO HOA, Zoned for Spring Hill Schools, minutes from GM, Saturn Pkway and I-65. So convienent to all shopping and dining. Some of the upgrades: Front Porch, Trex decking, cedar posts, Floors, Gas Tankless Water Heater, HVAC, Gas Oven/Stove, Dishwasher, all new lighting fixtures, Ceiling fans, New faucets, new toilets, new back door and Master bath fully renovated!! This property is in a league of its own, especially in this market!! Motivated Sellers!! Use Sellers preferred lender, April Barnes 615.260.39999 NMLS 186029 HRM , and get up to 1% towards closing costs or rate buy down. Not applicable for bond loans. Call for more details.
